href="how-to-set-your-token-allowances#revoking-allowances" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Revoking Allowances" title="Direct link to Revoking Allowances">â€‹</a></h2><p>To revoke an allowance, you can set the allowance to 0. This can be done programmatically or through a UI such as <a href="https://revoke.cash/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://revoke.cash/</a> .</p><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="common-issues">Common Issues<a href="how-to-set-your-token-allowances#common-issues" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Common Issues" title="Direct link to Common Issues">â€‹</a></h2><p>When setting the token allowance, make sure to provide enough allowance for the buy or sell amount <em>as well as the gas;</em> otherwise, you may receive a &#x27;Gas estimation failed&#x27; error.</p></div></article><nav class="pagination-nav docusaurus-mt-lg" aria-label="Docs pages navigation"><a class="pagination-nav__link pagination-nav__link--prev" href="rate-limiting"><div class="pagination-nav__sublabel">Previous</div><div class="pagination-nav__label">Rate Limiting</div></a><a class="pagination-nav__link pagination-nav__link--next" href="slippage-protection"><div class="pagination-nav__sublabel">Next</div><div class="pagination-nav__label">Slippage Protection</div></a></nav></div></div><div class="col col--3"><div class="tableOfContents_bqdL thin-scrollbar theme-doc-toc-desktop"><ul class="table-of-contents table-of-contents__left-border"><li><a href="how-to-set-your-token-allowances#setting-allowances-for-0x-api-quotes" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Setting Allowances for 0x API quotes</a><ul><li><a href="how-to-set-your-token-allowances#using-wagmi" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Using wagmi</a></li><li><a href="how-to-set-your-token-allowances#using-web3js" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Using web3.js</a></li><li><a href="how-to-set-your-token-allowances#using-etherscan" cl